data.tableSchema:
CREATE TABLE `stockmarket`.`stock_amarket_industry` (
	`updateDate` DATE   NOT NULL    COMMENT '记录上市公司行业变更日期' ,
	`codeno` MEDIUMINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票代码 定义为整型用于数据库关联检索' ,
	`symbol` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票代码' ,
	`stockcode` CHAR(9) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '证券代码 [股票代码.市场]' ,
	`stockmarketarea` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属市场 例如:上证指数，深证指数，科创板，创业板' ,
	`stockmarketareacode` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属编码 例如:sh_index,sz_index' ,
	`stockmarketareano` SMALLINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属市场编号检索字段 例如:1上海，2深圳，3科创板，4创业板' ,
	`stockname` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票名称' ,
	`industry` VARCHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '所属行业' ,
	`industryClassification` VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '行业分类' ,
	PRIMARY KEY  (`updateDate`,`codeno`)  
) ENGINE=InnoDB COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT='A股市场行业分类';

CREATE TABLE `stockmarket`.`stock_basic_ash` (
	`codeno` MEDIUMINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票代码  股票代码 定义为整型用于数据库关联检索' ,
	`stockcode` CHAR(9) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '证券代码 [股票代码.市场]' ,
	`symbol` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票代码' ,
	`stockmarketarea` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属市场 例如:上证指数，深证指数，科创板，创业板' ,
	`stockmarketareacode` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属编码 例如:sh_index,sz_index' ,
	`stockmarketareano` SMALLINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属市场编号检索字段 例如:1上海，2深圳，3科创板，4创业板' ,
	`stockname` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票名称' ,
	`area` CHAR(4) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '所在地域' ,
	`industry` VARCHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '所属行业' ,
	`stockfullname` VARCHAR(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票全称' ,
	`stockenfullname` VARCHAR(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '英文全称' ,
	`stockmarkettype` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '市场类型 （主板/中小板/创业板/科创板/CDR）' ,
	`exchange` CHAR(4) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '交易所代码' ,
	`curr_type` CHAR(3) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '交易货币' ,
	`list_status` CHAR(1) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '上市状态： L上市 D退市 P暂停上市' ,
	`list_date` DATE   NOT NULL    COMMENT '上市日期' ,
	`delist_date` DATE   NULL    COMMENT '退市日期' ,
	`is_hs` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '是否沪深港通标的，N否 H沪股通 S深股通' ,
	PRIMARY KEY  (`codeno`)  
) ENGINE=InnoDB COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT='股票基本信息';

CREATE TABLE `stockmarket`.`cache_r_industry_stock_sw` (
	`codeno` MEDIUMINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票编码 定义为整型用于数据库关联检索' ,
	`symbol` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '股票代码' ,
	`stockcode` CHAR(9) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '证券代码 [股票代码.市场]' ,
	`stockname` CHAR(15) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '股票名称' ,
	`indexcode` MEDIUMINT   NULL    COMMENT '指数编码' ,
	PRIMARY KEY  (`codeno`)  
) ENGINE=InnoDB COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT='申万行业指数与个股缓存表';

CREATE TABLE `stockmarket`.`ts_sw_index_r_member` (
	`indexcodeprefix` MEDIUMINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '指数代码前缀' ,
	`codeno` MEDIUMINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票编码 定义为整型用于数据库关联检索' ,
	`indexcode` CHAR(9) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '指数代码 [指数代码.发布机构]' ,
	`indexcodesuffix` CHAR(2) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '指数代码后缀' ,
	`industryname` CHAR(30) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '行业名称' ,
	`stockcode` CHAR(9) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '证券代码 [股票代码.市场]' ,
	`symbol` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票代码' ,
	`stockmarketareacode` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属编码 例如:sh,sz' ,
	`stockname` CHAR(20) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票名称' ,
	`indate` DATE   NULL    COMMENT '纳入日期' ,
	`outdate` DATE   NULL    COMMENT '剔除日期' ,
	`isnew` CHAR(1) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '是否最新Y是N否' ,
	PRIMARY KEY  (`indexcodeprefix`,`codeno`)  
) ENGINE=InnoDB COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT='TS申万行业成分';

CREATE TABLE `stockmarket`.`ts_new_share` (
	`stockcode` CHAR(9) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT 'ts证券代码 [股票代码.市场]' ,
	`symbol` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票代码' ,
	`stockmarketarea` CHAR(6) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属市场 例如:上证指数，深证指数，科创板，创业板' ,
	`stockmarketareacode` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属编码 例如:sh_index,sz_index' ,
	`stockmarketareano` SMALLINT   NOT NULL    COMMENT '股票所属市场编号检索字段 例如:1上海，2深圳，3科创板，4创业板' ,
	`subcode` CHAR(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '申购代码' ,
	`subname` VARCHAR(20) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '名称' ,
	`ipodate` DATE   NULL    COMMENT '上网发行日期' ,
	`issuedate` CHAR(8) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL    COMMENT '上市日期' ,
	`amount` DECIMAL(12,3)   NULL    COMMENT '发行总量（万股）' ,
	`marketamount` DECIMAL(12,3)   NULL    COMMENT '上网发行总量（万股）' ,
	`price` DECIMAL(8,2)   NULL    COMMENT '发行价格' ,
	`peTTM` DECIMAL(8,2)   NULL    COMMENT '市盈率' ,
	`limitamount` DECIMAL(8,2)   NULL    COMMENT '个人申购上限（万股）' ,
	`funds` DECIMAL(9,3)   NULL    COMMENT '募集资金（亿元）' ,
	`ballot` DECIMAL(5,2)   NULL    COMMENT '中签率' ,
	PRIMARY KEY  (`stockcode`)  
) ENGINE=InnoDB COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT='TSIPO新股列表';
